WILD symbol appears only on reels 2, 3, 4 and 5.
Whenever a WILD symbol hits it can have a random multiplier of 2x or 3x. If more than one wild is part of a winning combination, multipliers multiply each other.

Depending on the number of SCATTER symbols that trigger the feature, a different number of FREE SPINS is awarded:
20 free spins, from 3 to 7 sticky wilds on each reel
15 free spins, from 2 to 7 sticky wilds on each reel
12 free spins, from 2 to 7 sticky wilds on each reel
7 free spins, from 2 to 7 sticky wilds on each reel

During the round whenever a WILD symbol of any size hits, it gets a random multiplier of 1x, 2x or 3x and it remains on the reels until the end of the round, changing size as reel size changes in subsequent spins.
The feature can not be retriggered.
Depending on the number of SCATTER symbols that trigger the feature, a different number of FREE SPINS is awarded:
30 free spins with up to 6 raining wilds on each spin
25 free spins with up to 6 raining wilds on each spin
18 free spins with up to 6 raining wilds on each spin
15 free spins with up to 6 raining wilds on each spin
During the round at every spin up to 6 WILD symbols of any size, carrying a multiplier of 1x, 2x or 3x can be added to the screen in random positions.
The feature can not be retriggered.
Special reels are in play during FREE SPINS feature.

The FREE SPINS ROUND along with the FREE SPINS options can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet. On any buy a random number of SCATTER symbols, from 3 to 6 can hit to trigger the feature.
Hit 3 or more SCATTER symbols anywhere on the reels to trigger the FREE SPINS ROUND
Until the end of the round each reel size is guaranteed to be at minimum the size of the number of WILDS symbols sticky on it.
